long before the novelty fling adds a few more sparks than she was hoping for.  Fortuately for her, this surprise twist in the plot will thrust her back into the greatest role of her life.","poster_path":"/wiJp4pN2bYgtWQqZYZhGNLeFmx8.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"en","genre_ids":[35,18,10749],"popularity":1.4078,"release_date":"2004-09-03","softcore":false,"video":true,"vote_average":6.401,"vote_count":121}]},{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":2933404,"known_for_department":"Art","name":"István Szabó","original_name":"István Szabó","popularity":0.0,"profile_path":null,"known_for":[{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/aBY4QcxdLgaGLf3ZHUvuKjRm8yF.jpg","id":324560,"title":"Brimstone","original_title":"Brimstone","overview":"In the menacing inferno of the old North-American West, Liz is a genuine survivor who is hunted by a vengeful preacher for a crime she didn’t commit.","poster_path":"/aNxU4eZrfiChOgCEtyKWSCExdEi.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"en","genre_ids":[53,37,18],"popularity":3.7781,"release_date":"2016-03-12","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":7.154,"vote_count":1272}]},{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":3752350,"known_for_department":"Directing","name":"István Szabó","original_name":"István Szabó","popularity":0.0071,"profile_path":null,"known_for":[]},{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":3484906,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Istvan Szabo","original_name":"Istvan Szabo","popularity":0.0,"profile_path":null,"known_for":[{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"id":229535,"title":"Forced March","original_title":"Forced March","overview":"Ben Kline is an American television star and a bankable name, who is cast to portray the Hungarian writer Miklos Radnoti, whose journal of poems was found with his body, buried in one of Hungary’s mass graves. Kline is also the son of a Holocaust survivor and has long resented his father’s refusal to speak about the War. Now given the opportunity to play the role of a hero, but faced with the reality of a victim, the boundaries between truth and illusion begin to blur.","poster_path":"/m7MxEHjDWOol6h7oHF2UZsvs3V3.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"en","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.4045,"release_date":"1989-11-03","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":6.6,"vote_count":5}]},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":2041439,"known_for_department":"Writing","name":"István Sz. Szabó","original_name":"Sz. Szabó István","popularity":0.0168,"profile_path":null,"known_for":[{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/i3GjcU3TwK6lJobYDRjH9UX44Fc.jpg","id":523943,"title":"A galamb papné","original_title":"A galamb papné","overview":"The reformed priest of Gát, Pap Énók, gets married. He is engaged to the worthy Miss Ica Zádor from Malomsk and Zádor. At the Easter 'priestess election ball', Énók could have chosen a wife from among thirty-five Gáti girls, but he asked the thirty-sixth, Ica, a young lady from Pest. Enoch, of peasant origin, had studied his way up to the middle-class intellectuals of the countryside. Ica, the scion of a ruined noble family, comes from Budapest to a low-class marriage, but Ica's rise to office could bring her back into the higher social circles she had lost through the family's decline. They married for love, but both were guided by interest and expectation. Ica is a vivacious woman of the world, dissatisfied, bored, longing to return to life and society in Pest. She finds strange amusements: sometimes she embraces, sometimes she torments her master. Enoch is head over heels in love, puts up with everything, and in return happily accepts the kisses he is rewarded with.","poster_path":"/ju4QuhCa2viKbimSkZEwHLnjfVW.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"hu","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.0857,"release_date":"2013-12-25","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":8.5,"vote_count":1},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/3MtgV2oACmsScR9DDuDmABvNyZS.jpg","id":535141,"title":"A színésznő","original_title":"A színésznő","overview":"Anna, a celebrated Transylvanian actress starring at Hungary’s National Theatre in the mid-1960s, falls in love with an Olympic champion she meets at a reception, much to the regime’s displeasure, which has other plans for the multilingual star as an official hostess for visiting dignitaries. As the secret service weaves its manipulative web across every facet of her life, Anna, fortified by her love, proves a formidable opponent to their schemes.","poster_path":"/d3THWIH2qStuhEsQpDNnuv3ikuD.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"hu","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.0413,"release_date":"2018-04-07","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":8.0,"vote_count":1},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/fMuJzMy5MqFs2R4MsFeZyqjeSvp.jpg","id":523948,"title":"Pillangó","original_title":"Pillangó","overview":"Zsigmond Móricz wrote his novel Butterfly in just a few days in 1924. Móricz tells the story of a mighty love that triumphs over adversity and is all-powerful in the language of ordinary people. The love of Zsuzsika and Jóska is presented through the \"lightning and veil-soft\" emotions of the director, László Vitézy's television adaptation. After The Legend of Hortobágy (Komorló) and The Sky Bird, this is the third film made by László Vitézy based on the writings of Zsigmond Móricz.","poster_path":"/fXHMzuu50F9A4q9h0q7jPydh1hM.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"hu","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":0.3338,"release_date":"2012-12-26","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":0.0,"vote_count":0}]},{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":3102070,"known_for_department":"Writing","name":"Sz. Szabó István","original_name":"Sz. Szabó István","popularity":0.0143,"profile_path":null,"known_for":[{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"id":816592,"title":"Égi madár","original_title":"Égi madár","overview":"Panni becomes the wife of the landowner Komáromi and thus the first woman of the village. Marriage only brings her wealth, she does not love her lord, her new family despises her, and she does not even get a maid from her former girlfriends. His old lover, Miska, unexpectedly returns to the village and visits the woman. Panni receives him with a smile and, after mutual recriminations, expels him. She tells her husband everything, but Komáromi, unmanly, does not defend his wife himself, but throws Mishka out of the ball with others, and she hates him forever. When Panni meets Miska again, she refuses to let him go back to Pest alone. Another adaptation of Zsigmond Móricz's work.","poster_path":"/x6FJgWcRXF8EJTv1ifcGarghMhW.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"hu","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.144,"release_date":"2011-12-25","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":3.5,"vote_count":0}]},{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":1352550,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"István O. Szabó","original_name":"István O. Szabó","popularity":0.0168,"profile_path":"/AewLKRDGK8i5hHH9VRgM6Deflyu.jpg","known_for":[{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/pvakbkFa5O9eExGGK1BeuyLOwrP.jpg","id":202779,"title":"Hungarians","original_title":"Magyarok","overview":"A group of landless Hungarian peasants accept work as migrant-laborers on a farm in northern Germany where the wages are good, and the wives and family are allowed to accompany them. Though it is in the midst of World War II, they are relatively well-off. However, they glimpse the treatment accorded to POWs and others who are not so gently treated, and at the conclusion of the year's harvest, they choose to return to Hungary and are quickly swept up in the tides of war. This film is part of a series of films by award-winning, well-respected director Zoltan Fabri who devoted much time and effort chronicling the struggle against fascism.","poster_path":"/wu7YBSqs69RylJeEqOOBvBxze9y.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"hu","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.4252,"release_date":"1978-06-22","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":6.6,"vote_count":9},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/8T7qCL6MhZMF287WX9FxHRgmKBV.jpg","id":610646,"title":"Appassionata","original_title":"Appassionata","overview":"In the tragic autumn of 1944, the possibility of liberation from the war and the chains of the German alliance flashes before our eyes. Lacking leadership, in the first few hours people cannot yet know that their hopes are dashed, and they prepare the country not for celebration, but for burial. Some of the soldiers defect to the advancing Soviet forces, while others reload their weapons. A small group chooses a third path: they flee the front and try to fight their way home through adventurous journeys and encounters.","poster_path":"/3NmxjxBnuNplDkFrARBM40QQvl5.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"hu","genre_ids":[10752,18],"popularity":0.0746,"release_date":"1984-12-04","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":10.0,"vote_count":1},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"id":286474,"title":"Bálint Fábián Meets God","original_title":"Fábián Bálint találkozása Istennel","overview":"1918. Fábián Bálint is forced to kill humans on the Italian front. At home his sons drown the priest, the lover of their mother, in the river Kraszna. Mrs. Fábián turns insane. Following his arrival home Bálint becomes the liveried coachman of the baron.","poster_path":"/6wjPUPwFsUGTmFyVbAxpmZurPWt.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"hu","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.0798,"release_date":"1980-03-20","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":7.5,"vote_count":2}]},{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":2666994,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"István Szegedi Szabó","original_name":"István Szegedi Szabó","popularity":0.0071,"profile_path":null,"known_for":[{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"id":262614,"title":"Something Is in the Water","original_title":"Valamit visz a víz","overview":"A mysterious woman brings disaster to a small country town.","poster_path":"/qIsVz40neVtErTyJLUKmZZYzEV7.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"hu","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.0546,"release_date":"1944-01-26","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":6.0,"vote_count":4},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/ojmph3EiYEPK2mgn3taI9No0vH5.jpg","id":199521,"title":"A Strange Marriage","original_title":"Különös házasság","overview":"Count János Buttler rushes home to his parents and his beloved for the school holidays. On the way, they stop at Baron Dőry's house, where János is deviously trapped. In the presence of false witnesses, he is forcibly married to Baron Dőry's pregnant daughter. The swearing priest is the father of the unborn child. Although Buttler, his family and friends do their utmost to have the marriage annulled, the Church and the court, fearing for his authority, will not allow it. John Buttler and his lover therefore choose another way to divorce.","poster_path":"/ojoKl9dUkIkZMwFNwJDKoJVLQL5.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"en","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.1998,"release_date":"1951-08-12","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":8.0,"vote_count":2},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/lMN3boctamTtz1nUDZwlPFCVx4.jpg","id":540738,"title":"Military Band","original_title":"Katonazene","overview":"Merry soldiers arrive in the sleepy Transdanubian town. The cynical woman-hunter, Ferdinándy, learns to know doctor Barlay's beautiful wife at a carnival. She lives a happy married life, and the attentions of the lieutenant are all in vain.","poster_path":"/mjrvX7IgEvmnZnJkkAZeBqWWQ9b.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"hu","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.2057,"release_date":"1961-09-28","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":8.5,"vote_count":2}]},{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":2345194,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"O. Szabó István","original_name":"O. Szabó István","popularity":0.0,"profile_path":null,"known_for":[]},{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":2545846,"known_for_department":"Directing","name":"Márton István Szabó","original_name":"Márton István Szabó","popularity":0.11,"pr